      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to eliminate common floor pan fatigue. The chassis remains taut, retaining its factory-spec damping and Variable M Differential Lock functionality. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a flawless interior, this is a mechanically sorted, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
